<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background:inherit; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">The Road to Serfdom <span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Road+to+Serfdom&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BFriedrich+Hayek%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=March+1944&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BRoutledge%7CRoutledge+Press%5D%5D+%28UK%29%2C+%5B%5BUniversity+of+Chicago+Press%5D%5D+%28US%29&amp;rft.pages=266">&#160;</span></td>
